com.amazonaws.annotation

Annotation Type Beta


  • @Documented
 @Target(value={TYPE,METHOD})
 @Retention(value=CLASS)
public @interface Beta
    The class or method to which this annotation is applied is in beta mode. This means the annotated class or method is a relatively new API that may have bugs, complexity and usability issues that we have not fully anticipated. We will remove this annotation from the class or method once things get more settled.
